"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 05, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ato1665702863414.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ato1665702863414.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ato1665702863414.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ato1665702863414\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      &lt;x-option&gt;\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ato1665702863414___x_option__387894\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Uniface-specific XHTML tag that enables or disables a specific type of substitution tag (<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-subst&gt;</code>) for the whole static server page.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ato1665702863414__topic_d115571e1_d115572e1_d115573e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ato1665702863414__p_d115574e1_d115575e1_d115576e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-option</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">SubstitutionType</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=\"true\"</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"false\"&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<div class=\"example\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ato1665702863414__p_d115577e1_d115578e1_d115579e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-option inclFile=\"false\"\n               /&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ato1665702863414__topic_d82002e1_d82003e1_d82004e1_d82005e1_d82006e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d841042e83\">\n                       \n Arguments\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ato1665702863414__li_d44081e1_d44082e1_d44083e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ato1665702863414__p_d115583e1_d115584e1_d115585e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">SubstitutionType</var>—supported value of the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">type</span> attribute of a <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-subst&gt;</code> tag. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bxj1719470647227.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bxj1719470647227.html\" title=\"The &lt;x-subst&gt; element is a placeholder for an HTML element that will be generated in the HTML for a static server page (USP). It determines the location, type, and attributes of the HTML element that will be substituted.\">&lt;x-subst&gt;</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ato1665702863414__li_d44084e1_d44085e1_d44086e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ato1665702863414__p_d115586e1_d115587e1_d115588e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Boolean</var>—Uniface Boolean value, that is, TRUE or FALSE (or their equivalents).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ato1665702863414__topic_d82007e1_d82008e1_d82009e1_d82010e1_d82011e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d841042e126\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ato1665702863414__p_d115592e1_d115593e1_d115594e1\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-option&gt;</code> tag modifies the behavior of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webgen</span>, and so affects the entire web page.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ato1665702863414__p_d115595e1_d115596e1_d115597e1\">By default, all types of substitution tags (<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-subst&gt;</code>) in the server page are enabled. You can use the <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;option&gt;</code> tag to disable a specific type of substitution, but this will then be applied to all substitutions of the same type. It is not possible to disable a substitution type at one point in server page and then enable it at a later point.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ato1665702863414__p_d115598e1_d115599e1_d115600e1\">For example, if your server page includes several substitution tags to include files (<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-subst type=\"inclFile\" name=\"../js/myjs1.js\"&gt;</code>), setting <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-option inclFile=\"false\"&gt;</code> will mean that none of your files will be included in the resulting HTML.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gna1665702540285.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>webgen</a><p>Generate an XHTML document from the layout definition and the component definition of a static server page.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525871\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525871\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "<x-option> Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 05, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 <x-option> Uniface-specific XHTML tag that enables or disables a specific type of substitution tag ( <x-subst> ) for the whole static server page. <x-option SubstitutionType =\"true\" | \"false\"> Example: <x-option inclFile=\"false\" /> Arguments SubstitutionType —supported value of the type attribute of a <x-subst> tag. For more information, see <x-subst> . Boolean —Uniface Boolean value, that is, TRUE or FALSE (or their equivalents). Description The <x-option> tag modifies the behavior of webgen , and so affects the entire web page. By default, all types of substitution tags ( <x-subst> ) in the server page are enabled. You can use the <option> tag to disable a specific type of substitution, but this will then be applied to all substitutions of the same type. It is not possible to disable a substitution type at one point in server page and then enable it at a later point. For example, if your server page includes several substitution tags to include files ( <x-subst type=\"inclFile\" name=\"../js/myjs1.js\"> ), setting <x-option inclFile=\"false\"> will mean that none of your files will be included in the resulting HTML. Related Links webgen Generate an XHTML document from the layout definition and the component definition of a static server page. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}